org.glassfish.api.admin

Interface CommandParameters

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DeployCommand, DeployCommandParameters, DeployDirCommand, DeployRemoteArchiveCommand, DisableCommand, EnableCommand, InstanceDeployCommand, InstanceDeployCommandParameters, InstanceRegisterInstanceCommand, InstanceRegisterInstanceCommandParameters, OpsParams, PostDeployCommand, PostRegisterInstanceCommand, PostUndeployCommand, ReDeployCommand, RegisterInstanceCommandParameters, StateCommandParameters, UndeployCommand, UndeployCommandParameters, ValidateRemoteDirDeploymentCommand

    public interface CommandParameters
    A marker interface to indicate classes that are used to pass parameters to the parameters method of the CommandRunner.CommandInvocation API. Classes marked as CommandParameters should declare public fields whose name is the parameter name and whose value is the parameter value.
